# Authority & determinism

- Frozen stage order; log every stage in `manifest.json`
- Precedence: window override > consensus > single-signal
- Geometry sources resolve deterministically; never invent positions/areas/turns
- Generated FreeGSNKE scripts must read `execution_authority_bundle.json` (fail-fast if missing)
- Template rendering: token substitution only (`__TOKEN__`), never `str.format` on Python templates
- Residual budget buckets that are unmeasured must be `UNMEASURED`, not `0.0`
- Coil mapping: explicit `coil_map` only for production; heuristics may suggest, not silently apply
